## Supplementary Figure 8E-Developmental Plasticity and Senescence Scores

Comparison of plasticity and senescence enrichment scores across developmental stages.

### Workflow

- Plasticity-associated gene signatures were adapted from He et al.
- Senescence-associated gene signatures were compiled from established senescence markers.
- Gene set enrichment scores were calculated for each developmental stage.
- Scores were visualized to compare developmental plasticity and senescence dynamics.

### Software

- R
- Seurat
- GSVA
- ggplot2
